:: Cafe [nobr]
<<set $gamelocation to "Cafe">>

You enter a large cafe for eating.


<span id="foodMenuUI"><<FoodMenuUI>></span>

<<unset $spawnPools>>
<<run setup.refreshFullPool()>>
<<SpawnPoolOnce "fullPool" $fullPool 15>>
<<SpawnRandomNPCs 15>>

<<include "NPC-List">>

